OL,7,FAn accountant who killed his wife
OL,8,Fwhile he was experiencing a psychotic
OL,9,Fepisode has been detained in hospital
OL,10,Findefinitely.
OL,12,FDarryl Bowen, 43, pleaded guilty to
OL,13,Fmanslaughter by diminished
OL,14,Fresponsibility for fatally stabbing
OL,15,FAlison Bowen, 41, at their home in
OL,16,FKingswood, Bristol, in November last
OL,17,Fyear.
