OL,7,FBristol Crown Court heard Bowen, who
OL,8,Fhas since been diagnosed with paranoid
OL,9,Fschizophrenia, was experiencing an
OL,10,Facute episode of psychosis at the time.
OL,12,FSentencing him at Bristol Crown Court,
OL,13,FJudge Julian Lambert said Bowen was
OL,14,Fsuffering from religious delusions
OL,15,Fwhen he attacked his wife and was
OL,16,F"labouring under the false belief that
OL,17,Fthe world was coming to an end".
OL,19,FBowen's defence counsel said he
OL,20,Fexperienced "bewilderment" at his
OL,21,Factions.
