OL,7,FThe judge described Ms Bowen as a
OL,8,F"wonderful daughter, beloved sister
OL,9,Fand a kind and devoted wife," who was
OL,10,F"loving and nurturing".
OL,12,F"She had friends across the world and
OL,13,Fwas a beacon of hope and probity to
OL,14,Fmany. She was simply an inspirational
OL,15,Fhuman being," he added.
OL,17,FThe judge said: "I find it difficult
OL,18,Fto describe the epic depth of the
OL,19,Ftragedy in this case. This was the
OL,20,Fultimate betrayal of your wife.
