OL,7,F"It is a struggle ever to understand
OL,8,Fhow the mind of a husband and devout
OL,9,Fchurchgoer became so distorted that he
OL,10,Fcould have done this.
OL,12,F"The origin of such disorder is beyond
OL,13,Fmy powers of understanding but there
OL,14,Fis now no doubt you were deeply
OL,15,Fdeluded and very ill. You remain ill
OL,16,Fand your recovery is uncertain."
