OL,7,FThe judge added that psychiatrists who
OL,8,Fhad examined Bowen agreed he was
OL,9,Fsuffering from severe mental illness,
OL,10,Fpossibly caused by "significant" work-
OL,11,Frelated stress.
OL,13,FAndrew Langdon KC, prosecuting, told
OL,14,Fhow Bowen previously had a psychiatric
OL,15,Fepisode and spent time in hospital in
OL,16,F2004 but was released from the mental
OL,17,Fhealth team in 2008, after becoming
OL,18,Fsymptom-free.
OL,20,FIn August 2023, Bowen contacted his GP
OL,21,Fdue to experiencing stress at work.
