OL,7,FOn the day before Mrs Bowen's death,
OL,8,FBowen was seen acting in a "bizarre
OL,9,Fand disturbed" manner in a restaurant.
OL,11,FMr Langdon said Bowen fatally stabbed
OL,12,Fhis wife with a kitchen knife on 20
OL,13,FNovember last year, after she asked to
OL,14,Fcall their pastor when he attempted to
OL,15,Fcut cables in their home.
OL,17,FThe judge said: "Given your offending,
OL,18,Frecent behaviour and your psychiatric
OL,19,Fcondition, I can only find that you
OL,20,Fare dangerous and will be so for a
OL,21,Flong time."
