OL,7,FBowen, who appeared before the court
OL,8,Fvia video link from hospital, will not
OL,9,Fbe released without the permission of
OL,10,Fthe Ministry of Justice, or a tribunal.
OL,12,FSpeaking after sentencing, Mrs Bowen's
OL,13,Ffamily said: "We are devastated that
OL,14,FAlison has been killed and, although
OL,15,Fwe cannot repair what has been done to
OL,16,Fher and to our family, we are all
OL,17,Fpulling together to help each other as
OL,18,Fwe move forward.
